    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>High-melting brazing alloy, typically brass with silver, requiring temperatures ranging between 750 and 900 degrees Celsius to melt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
